  <bioghist id="aspace_ee64eb9559d05ed38b590252ff9e587a" encodinganalog="545$a">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Texas railroads began in 1852 with the first tracks laid, and became more prevalent in the 1860s and 1870s.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_9dca4fd920712b0427c77335f7317ed6" encodinganalog="520$b">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>Pamphlets and documents documenting the history of Texas railroad lines such as Houston &amp; Texas Central Railroad Co., Texas &amp; Pacific Railway Co., Texas &amp; New Orleans Railroad Co., Galveston, Harrisburg &amp; San Antonio Railway Co.</p>  </scopecontent>
